headline: T. ROWE PRICE GROUP REPORTS PRELIMINARY MONTH-END ASSETS UNDER MANAGEMENT FOR APRIL 2025
summary: T. Rowe Price Group, Inc. (NASDAQ-GS: TROW), today reported preliminary month-end assets under management of $1.56 trillion as of April 30, 2025. Preliminary net outflows for April 2025 were $3.5 billion.
